abstract: Australia beats New Zealand by seven wickets to sweep series, 2-0, and regain status as No 1 Test cricket nation.

headline.main: Australia Is Once Again No. 1 in Test Cricket

snippet: Australia reclaimed the No. 1 ranking among Test cricket nations, from India, when it beat New Zealand in Christchurch by seven wickets.
lead_paragraph: Australia reclaimed the No. 1 ranking among Test cricket nations, from India, when it beat New Zealand in Christchurch by seven wickets.
